{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-04_038", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Vers à Iris]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", avril 1678 [tome 4], p. 38-40."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je ne doute point que vous n’en [de l’Esprit] trouviez beaucoup dans les Vers qui suivent. Je les croy de Mr Cordetz. Vous avez veu son nom parmy ceux qui ont deviné les Enigmes. Le détour qu’il prend est galant & il seroit difficile d’imaginer une maniere plus adroite de faire une déclaration d’amour à une Belle, qu’en s’adressant d’abord comme il a fait à un Enfant."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "À Mademoiselle H."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[2]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[2]/text()[1]", "text": "la Cadette, âgée de quatre à cinq ans."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Jeune Iris que mon cœur adore,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Et dont tous mes sens sont charmez,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Chacun me dit que vous m’aimez,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais je ne le puis croire encore."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Si de ma passion le tendre empressement"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "M’acquiert le bonheur de vous plaire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Aimez-moy passionnément"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Tandis que vous le pouvez faire."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "À vostre âge l’Amour n’est pas un grand defaut :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Aimez, puis que ce dieu vous a si-tost émeuë."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Le temps ne viendra que trop tost."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Où vous serez plus retenuë."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "S’il est quelques douceurs que vous vouliez de moy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Expliquez vous en sans contrainte."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Puis que je vous donne ma foy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous pouvez demander tout le reste sans crainte."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Souffrez un tel discours de la part d’un Amant,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "Vostre âge luy permet de dire ce qu’il pense,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[19]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[19]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[19]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais dans dix ans en récompense"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[20]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[20]/text()[1]", "text": "Il se verra réduit à parler autrement."}]}]}]}